This looks like a similar problem I had two days back.  It was fixed in my case
by cleaning and then installing a new build (such as TPTP-4.1.0-200510121143).

"org.eclipse.hyades.test.core was unable to load class 
org.eclipse.hyades.execution.harness.DebugExecutableObjectStub."
I tried to install a new build and I can still see the problem

I had to completely remove everything and install the entire stack, Eclipse, 
EMF, XSD, TPTP, agent controller, perhaps this is what you have done as well -- 
I will assign it to Julien, I think (please correct me if I'm wrong Julien) he 
had been delivering files in this area recently.

I only replaced the TPTP plugins and RAC runtime; I used the same eclipse, 
emf, xsd ( under the same location )

Using build TPTP-4.1.0-200510130737, I couldn't reproduce these specific problems.
